               <msContents>
                  <summary>Homiliary in Honor of the Archangel Michael, Dǝrsanä Mika’el, ድርሳነ፡ ሚካኤል፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Codex">
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>
                           <watermark/>
                        </support>
                        <extent>
                           <measure unit="leaf"/>
                           <dimensions type="outer" unit="mm">
                              <height/>
                              <width/>
                              <depth/>
                           </dimensions>
                        </extent>
                     </supportDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                  <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                  <seg type="rubrication">
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢግዚአብሔር፡</foreign>
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign>
                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word Michael is rubricated</desc>
                  </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#iir(ecto)"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1077ArchangelMichael"/> with <term key="sword"/> and <term key="scabbard"/></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d2">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#1r #12r #30v #35v #52v #60r #65r #75v #82r #91r #94v"/> (haräg);
                    <locus target="#11r #19r #20r #30v #31v #35v #52v #53v #57v #60r #65r #67r #73r #76v #80v #91r #93v #101r"/> (multiple full stops)
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#101r #101v #102r #102v #103r"/>: Catechism On the Five Pillars
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#103v"/>: Concluding <title type="complete" ref="LIT1295Dersan/main"/>, written in purple and pink inks
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#104v #105r"/>: Excerpts from various images of the saints
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#10v"/> and passim: the name of the owner, Wäldä Mädḫǝn, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ መድኅን፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#11r"/> and passim: the name of a second owner, Mänbärawit, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መንበራዊት፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a6">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#66v"/> and passim: mentions a new owner, Kǝflä Maryam, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክፍለ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a7">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#101r"/>: Colophon mentioning the owner, Wäldä Mädḫǝn, and the scribe, Kǝflä Maryam
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#iiv(erso) #104r #105v"/>: blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    Identified in the insurance hand list as Case A8
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
                    The codex has blue numbers on the bottom recto-side of the folio in the fashion of the EMML project
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention: words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#3r #3v #4r #4v #6r"/> etc.); and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#3r"/>, col. 2, line 5; <locus target="#6v"/>, col. 1, line 3; <locus target="#66v"/>, col. 1, line 7; <locus target="#78v"/>, col. 2, line 15; <locus target="#89r"/>, col. 2, line 10; <locus target="#92v"/>, col. 2, line 17); text has been removed (<locus target="#81r, 101r, 103r"/>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>

                  </list>
                  </additions>
